builds.pull_request_title: refactor(router-deprecated): avoid export of private name CanActivate

commit.message:
refactor(router-deprecated): avoid export of private name CanActivate

`router-deprecated/src/lifecycle/lifecycle_annotations.ts` imports
`CanActivate` under an alias and then re-exports a new variable
declaration under the **same name**. This **breaks the API doc
generation**. This simple refactoring renames the private `CanActivate`
to `CanActivateAnnotation`.
